body:
We know its coming some time in 2017. So what do you want to see? {{champion:19}} 

For me the things that are iconic to Warwick are attacking fast, built in life-steal/drain and the Blood Scent passive.

Blood Scent in particular is something that I think needs to stay. It is a fairly unique mechanic, unlike the rest of his kit, and I find it very satisfying when it triggers. Especially when it spots a wounded enemy that my teammate was trying to chase and I get to rush in and finish them off. It just really suits the kind of thing that a Warewolf should be doing.

Personally I think he could work really well as a Juggernaut, but keeping him as a Diver like he is now is also fine. I don&#039;t think it makes any sense to turn him into a Tank like Sion or Poppy.

What are your thoughts? {{champion:19}}

replies.body:
